CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1781291475
OL,3,CCouncillor who oversaw bin services
OL,4,Cduring strikes resigns from Labour
OL,5,CParty
OL,7,FThe councillor who oversaw bin
OL,8,Fservices during the bin strikes in
OL,9,FBirmingham has resigned from the
OL,10,FLabour Party.
OL,12,FCllr Majid Mahmood was in charge of
OL,13,Fthe city's waste management services
OL,14,Fwhen the ongoing strike action began
OL,15,Fmore than 18 months ago.
OL,17,FThe councillor for Bromford and Hodge
OL,18,FHill said he was resigning from the
OL,19,Fparty for several issues, including
OL,20,FLabour's current immigration policy
OL,21,Fand its stance on the conflict in Gaza.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1781291475
OL,3,CCouncillor who oversaw bin services
OL,4,Cduring strikes resigns from Labour
OL,5,CParty
OL,7,FIn a statement released on X, Cllr
OL,8,FMahmood said the party had become
OL,9,F"more managerial, centralised, and
OL,10,Fconstrained in its tolerance of
OL,11,Finternal difference, both locally and
OL,12,Fnationally".
OL,14,FHe continued: "For these reasons, I
OL,15,Fcan no longer remain a member in good
OL,16,Fconscience.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1781291475
OL,3,CCouncillor who oversaw bin services
OL,4,Cduring strikes resigns from Labour
OL,5,CParty
OL,7,F"I am also deeply concerned by the
OL,8,Fdirection of Labour's immigration
OL,9,Fpolicy, which appears increasingly
OL,10,Fshaped by political expediency rather
OL,11,Fthan principle or long-term vision.
OL,13,F"In conversations with residents in
OL,14,FBromford and Hodge Hill, this has been
OL,15,Fa recurring concern, with many
OL,16,Fexpressing anxieties about how recent
OL,17,Fpolicy shifts are being communicated
OL,18,Fand implemented, and a sense that
OL,19,Fcommunities like ours are often talked
OL,20,Fabout rather than listened to."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
