PN,37305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1781291475
OL,3,CCouncillor who oversaw bin services
OL,4,Cduring strikes resigns from Labour
OL,5,CParty
OL,7,F"In conversations with residents in
OL,8,FBromford and Hodge Hill, this has been
OL,9,Fa recurring concern, with many
OL,10,Fexpressing anxieties about how recent
OL,11,Fpolicy shifts are being communicated
OL,12,Fand implemented, and a sense that
OL,13,Fcommunities like ours are often talked
OL,14,Fabout rather than listened to."
OL,16,FAs well as the national party, Mahmood
OL,17,Fsaid he had "serious concerns about
OL,18,Fthe current state of the Birmingham
OL,19,FLabour Group.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
